ASoC: sgtl5000: Fix charge pump source assignment

If VDDA != VDDIO and any of them is greater than 3.1V, charge pump
source can be assigned automatically [1].

[1] https://www.nxp.com/docs/en/data-sheet/SGTL5000.pdf

